    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped as not-assessed per ASME V&V 40 Table 3 guidance for MRL 2. Validation results demonstrate NIH prediction within 8.4% MAPE of FDA benchmark data, satisfying the pre-specified 15% acceptance criterion. RH < 1 at all five operating points confirms identification of worst-case hemolysis conditions. The UQ campaign conducted as part of the validation activities confirmed low sensitivity of RH to dominant input uncertainties. Total evidence is sufficient to support the regulatory submission decision for the Class II CPB device.",
